  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="20182787">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/directerzhu/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1095114-8.jpg" alt="Director Zhu" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20182787/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20182787/" class="">第468页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/directerzhu/" class=" " title="Director Zhu">Director Zhu</a>
                (我是一场不明所以的战争。)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="20182787">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">有时爱不是通过欲望相和甚至不是通过幸福的平静之路实现的。爱的性质是坦率地寻求毁灭。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-08-06 23:37</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">5人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                有时爱不是通过欲望相和甚至不是通过幸福的平静之路实现的。爱的性质是坦率地寻求毁灭。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

